<strong>REFERENCE LIST ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference list at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
Include the name of the director as the author and the name of the production company as the 
publisher. A description of the work is provided in square brackets after the title. 
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent double-line-spacing">
	Director. (Year of publication). <em>Title of work</em> [Description]. Production Company.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent double-line-spacing">
	<span class="hover" title="Director">Jones, A. (Director)</span>. 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2020</span>). 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of work">Outside the lines</span></em> 
	[<span class="hover" title="Description">Film</span>]. 
	<span class="hover" title="Production Company">Upbeat Pictures</span>.
</blockquote>
